tulit] it should be remembered that tuli (tetuli) is strictly the perfect of tollo but is borrowed by fero which has properly speaking no perfect of its own: tollo uses forits perfect sustuli strictly a perfect of the rare present sustollo, and the same perfect is also borrowed to serve as the perfect of suffero.
